data.description: Well maintained ranch in Westbury Plan.  West Allegheny schools, close to shopping, restaurants and Pittsburgh Airport. Three bedrooms on the main level and a bonus room in the basement that could be used as an additional bedroom.  New windows and exterior doors, new trex deck, new flooring in the kitchen and living room, new kitchen cabinets, new concrete sidewalk to the house and partial new driveway. Tons of parking in the back and large shed for additional storage.
